<p>I was one of the four original founders. I participated in all the project phases, from the idea, to the launch. I was responsible for the gameplay, the graphics, and all the front-end development: the website and the web app.</p>

<h3>Mobile app</h3>
<p>I designed everything, from the interaction between screens, to the gameplay graphics. The mobile app is composed of four main sections accessible from the home screen: attack/defend your territory (map), the chat, the gang (team) page, and the store. Although, it was hard to navigate between sections, most use cases were only happening in the same sections, avoiding the need to navigate. You can see below a sample of the mobile wireframes I designed.</p>

