<h3>Web app</h3>
<p>I also designed the web app, which has never been fully developed. Because there is more real estate available on desktop, I was able to organize all sections on the same screen. The map is really the most important aspect of the game. That's why I decided to make it the central part of the app. Additional menus on the sides give contextual information when interacting with the map.</p>

